---

import risaGptsSvgUrl from "../assets/RisaGPT.svg?url";

const bullets = [
    "性格や趣味嗜好を設計した会話するGPTsを設計",
    "正解よりも共感を目指した設計"
];
const bulletsEn = [
    "GPTs designed for conversation — built with personality and preference in mind,",
    "and created to seek empathy, not correctness."
];
---
<section id="risagpts" class="rg-section">
    <div class="rg-container">
        <!-- 右：SVG（PC）／上：SVG（SP） -->
        <div class="visual-wrap">
            <div class="rg-glow" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <figure class="rg-frame" aria-label="Risa GPTs emblem">
                <img
                    src={risaGptsSvgUrl}
                    alt="Risa GPTs Collection"
                    class="rg-svg"
                    loading="lazy"
                    decoding="async"
                />
            </figure>
        </div>

        <!-- 左：テキスト（PC）／下：テキスト（SP） -->
        <header class="rg-head">
            <p class="eyebrow">AI Talent × GPTs</p>
            <h2 class="title">
                Risa GPTs
            </h2>
            <p class="lede">
                「Risa」は温かみのあるAIを目指す。<br />
                人のように感じ、<span>曖昧さや想い</span>に寄り添う。<br /><br />
                <span class="en">
                    “Risa aspires to be an AI with warmth.”<br />
                    To <span>feel and empathize</span> like a human, embracing ambiguity and emotion.
                </span>
            </p>
            <ul class="bullets">
                {bullets.map((b, i) => (
                    <li>
                        {b}<br />
                        <span class="en">{bulletsEn[i]}</span>
                    </li>
                ))}
            </ul>
            <div class="cta-row">
                <a
                    href="https://chatgpt.com/g/g-68f62ed3ddb48191a37f6c97b68e813b-risa-gpts"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noreferrer"
                    class="cta"
                >
                    View on GPTs
                </a>
            </div>
        </header>
    </div>
</section>

